        </li>
      </ol> 
      <p> 
        <hr /> <a name="first"></a><b>1. Stimulus Payments Update</b> 
        <hr /> 
      </p> 
      <p>Look for updates on the IRS.gov <a title="" href="http://www.irs.gov/newsroom/article/0,,id=177937,00.html" target="">stimulus payments</a> page, also available in <a title="" href="http://www.irs.gov/espanol/article/0,,id=180561,00.html" target="">Spanish</a>. 
      </p> 
      <p style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><a href="#top">Back to top</a> 
      </p> 
      <hr /> <a name="second"></a><b>2. Recent Disaster Relief</b> 
      <hr /> 
      <p>Victims of Tropical Storm Fay in <a title="" href="http://www.irs.gov/newsroom/article/0,,id=186300,00.html" target="">Florida</a> may qualify for IRS disaster relief. The IRS is also monitoring damage from Hurricane Gustav. Be sure to check for updates on the <a title="" href="http://www.irs.gov/newsroom/article/0,,id=108362,00.html" target="">tax relief in disaster situations</a> page. 
      </p> 
      <p style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><a href="#top">Back to top</a> 
      </p> 
