      </p> 
      <p style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><a href="#top">Back to top</a> 
      </p> 
      <hr /> <a name="fourth"></a><b>4. September Phone Forum for Practitioners</b> 
      <hr /> 
      <p>Check out the upcoming free <a title="" href="http://www.irs.gov/businesses/small/article/0,,id=158856,00.html#3" target="">phone forum</a> on Sept. 17. Find out about the field audit process and working toward a mutual commitment date. Sign up now and be sure to use the correct conference access code when registering. 
      </p> 
